reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I have worn this a few times and I really like how it accentuates my features. Its tight on the skin but not suffocatingly so. So far it has maintained its color as well/ Great product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I’m 5’4, 153 lbs, smaller in the waist, wider in the hips and the Medium fits perfectly. It hugs, tucks and lifts all the right places. The material is thick so it’s not see through if you bend. It’s nice enough that you can wear it with a nice blouse and heels or you can wear it casual. It works either way. Will definitely buy again.
